    "name": "SILENT SCREAM 2",
    "steam_appid": 3023460,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023460/extras/4b40983dc085a2e6099d2e9b2404af66.avif?t=1748327643\" width=616 height=357 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A horror mystery where the story unravels — and something else pushes through.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're invited to Midnight Castle for what should be a simple mystery retreat. Solve puzzles, explore eerie environments, and piece together clues as you work your way deeper into the castle's strange and sinister story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023460/extras/fd1e51d67c42611cd0fdc9e92b70299e.avif?t=1748327643\" width=616 height=87 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023460/extras/5948ab88fb432bd4ea158cb8d9cc6096.avif?t=1748327643\" width=616 height=171 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet a cast of flawed and unpredictable guests, each with their own reasons for attending — and their own secrets to keep. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023460/extras/d70c4483dc8a11798f2ec1a2ed5264ab.avif?t=1748327643\" width=616 height=70 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023460/extras/881de2f8e3a199c2d65e184ef51589fe.avif?t=1748327643\" width=616 height=555 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023460/extras/aa0550ccb0f74f567c2d86b9c7335820.webp?t=1748327643\" width=522 height=24 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Narrator guides your every move — sarcastic, defensive, and constantly scrambling to keep things running. Broken objects? Strange bugs? Missing UI? No problem (according to him). It’s all part of the experience… probably.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But something is... off.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023460/extras/9db536e64f01402d7f0b73dd6a018cec.webp?t=1748327643\" width=186 height=24 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the night unfolds, however, things start to slip. Glitches grow worse. Puzzles twist and change. And something foreign — something malicious — begins rewriting the game according to rules beyond understanding.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A guided horror adventure with an unreliable narrator and fourth-wall breaking narration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a mystery that spirals into chaos as the narrator's grip weakens. Navigate shifting realities, face unexpected threats, and survive the story’s collapse as Midnight Castle — and the game itself — fracture and distort.</p>",
